snippet.title: Red Rocket Defencism | 2nd Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2854440/Red_Rocket_Defencism/
✊Add to your wishlist for OUR GREAT MOTHERLAND✊

You, a military officer from our great autocratic motherland, must protect our precious rockets from the evil capitalist enemy in this revolutionary base building strategy game.
Bribe! Surveil! Purge! Imbibe! The end justifies the means when you have to protect our invaluable rockets!

Red Rocket Defencism
Coming to Steam in 2025.
